Nigerian actress, Ruth Kadiri welcomed her baby girl on Monday, and has since been receiving heart warming and congratulatory messages, from fellow actors, actresses, directors, producers and fans worldwide. The actress who posted a video on Instagram, some days before the delivery of her baby, revealed that she went through hell, days before labour. Elated Ruth said, “Our sweet baby girl Reign Nwachinemelu Ezerika made her way into this world on the 26 of August 2019. It still feels like a dream. I’m not the perfect girl, but I’m blessed to have the perfect gift at this time of my life. With love from mommy. Erhmmm daddy loves you. Congratulations to Ruth Kadiri on her new born baby.